title: FNC’s Kimberly Guilfoyle hopes ‘Snoop & wannabe-Snoop’ have to answer some questions [video]
text:
FNC’s Kimberly Guilfoyle hopes ‘Snoop & wannabe-Snoop’ have to answer some questions [video] Posted at 6:19 pm on March 16, 2017 by Doug P. 
A video by Snoop Dogg depicting the rapper pointing a gun at the head of a clown dressed as Donald Trump drew criticism from the president yesterday. After Trump slammed the video, Snoop Dogg protégé Bow Wow threatened to “pimp” Melania Trump in a tweet that was later deleted. 
The Five’s Kimberly Guilfoyle thinks some visits are in order: . @kimguilfoyle : "It would be fantastic if Snoop and wannabe-Snoop got a visit from the federal marshals." #TheFive pic.twitter.com/h7iNkH7uOP 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) March 16, 2017 Trending
